resources.string: Engeza iqoqo lakho lomuntu siqu Kubika lohlelo lwekhyomputha Lomcuno bese uwufinyelela ngaleso sikhathi kunoma iyiphi ikhyomputha exhunyiwe noma idivayisi ye-Android.
Xhuma idivayisi yakho kukhyomputha ngekhebuli le-USB ukuze ukupishe umculo kudivayisi yakho. Uma une-Macintosh, layisha uhlelo lokudlulisela Lwefayili le-Android kuqala kukhyomputha yakho.
Awukwazi ukusakaza umculo ngoba awuxhunyiwe kuhlelo xhumano lwedatha.
Kumelwe uxhumeke kuhleloxhumano lwe-WiFi ukuze usakaze umculo
